Install firefox if not already using

Install beautifulsoup using pip
pip could be installed already on your computer in iterm type in man pip if a manual page comes up you have pip installed
if not go into iterm and use sudo easy_install pip
terminal will prompt you for your loginpassword

once pip is installed in iterm type in: pip install beautifulsoup4

also install splinter
pip install splinter

within home directory type in nano .bash_profile
within .bash_profile type in
export PATH=$PATH:/folder where geckodriver located/geckodriver



edit main.py with your information
run main.py using python main.py in shopBOT folder
